<div></div>
<div>Skiing is for everyone - If you’re willing to learn and fancy an adventure, skiing is for you. </div>
<!--start here-->
<p>Inghams have a wealth of experience in the skiing and snowboarding industry and have introduced thousands of people to the fun and exciting world of snow sports over the years. We know where the best skiing destinations for beginners are and we are here to help point you in the direction. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a style="text-align: center;" data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" class="c-btn">View ski holiday deals</a></p>
<p>We are here with you every step of the way and we can help you arrange the following for your trip:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-hire">Ski and snowboard rentals </a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-lessons">Skiing and snowboarding lessons</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-lift-passes">Lift pass </a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-insurance">Ski insurance</a></li>
</ul>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Your holiday with Inghams</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 95px; height: 28px;" src="/media/13107196/whats-included-with-inghams.jpg?width=95&amp;height=28" alt="WhatsIncludedWithInghams" data-udi="umb://media/1075e5d667ab411580a93714ac65208f" /></p>
