<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Beginners ski holiday - visit France</h2>
<p><strong>France</strong> is the perfect destination if you are new to skiing or snowboarding. France offers gentle, wide slopes, a record for snowfall, plenty of ski schools or hire shops in all resorts and isn't too far to travel for your first attempt at the slopes. </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">La Plagne</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13082873/bea_8482.jpg" alt="LaPlagne" data-udi="umb://media/49b4a2f9956d4ecfa36b5f8619b32af4" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"></span><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a href="/{localLink:2ff87f97-1406-4899-8321-62705cd015d2}" title="Best Ski Resorts for Beginners"></a></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Part of the Paradiski ski area, one the largest in Europe</li>
<li>La Plagne has 70 blue runs for beginners to practice on</li>
<li>There are several beginners areas with green runs to build up confidence</li>
<li>Many off the blue runs lead off the mountain so new skiers can ski almost straight back to their accommodation</li>
<li>The Paradiski ski area has a total of 18 green runs and 129 blue runs so a week building skills and exploring here is easily done</li>
</ul>
<div class="data-grid" style="text-align: center;"><a style="font-weight: bold;" data-udi="umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c155a29773fd476189963f3b4e3b57e4}" title="La Plagne" class="c-btn">View La Plagne</a></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Tignes</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13082838/valdisere-00012753.jpg" alt="TignesResort" data-udi="umb://media/0b2ac54a1d1a4f92a5756972cf53d9ff" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a14e6dca75054857b291ea3f591dde09" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a14e6dca75054857b291ea3f591dde09}" title="Skiers code of conduct"></a></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Designated nursery areas for little ones learning to ski, where you can help them practice safely with other similar level children</li>
<li>An impressive 25 green and 65 blue runs can be found across the Tignes/Val d'Isere ski area, so plenty of space to explore</li>
<li>Tignes has plenty of wide, cruising blues to help build your confidence close to the resort</li>
<li>There is a 'beginners only' area for those learning or joining ski lessons</li>
<li>There are 9 free lifts across Tignes resort, meaning you can build up your skills without the cost</li>
</ul>
<div class="data-grid" style="text-align: center;"><a style="font-weight: bold;" data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes" class="c-btn">View Tignes</a></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Courchevel</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13092663/courchevel-fashion-chairlift-858x408.jpg" alt="CourchevelResort" data-udi="umb://media/54ce82117db642a5baad2cc355120aa3" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a data-udi="umb://document/58e77a234056413da253b6cdafad6660" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58e77a234056413da253b6cdafad6660}" title="What to wear for skiing"></a></span></p>
<ul>
<li>One the larger French resorts, offering access to 53 green runs and 137 blue runs - you will soon build up the confidence here</li>
<li>Courchevel is part of the Three Valleys ski area in France, which is the largest linked ski area in Europe</li>
<li>There are several 'ZEN areas' that are perfect for beginners and has been designed to help anyone learn to ski or snowboard</li>
<li>The ski schools here are very good and have many English speaking tutors to help assit your progression</li>
</ul>
<div class="data-grid" style="text-align: center;"><a style="font-weight: bold;" data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel" class="c-btn">View Courchevel</a></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"></span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Flaine</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13099597/dsc01292-1.jpg" alt="FlaineResort" data-udi="umb://media/79b47bb375ac48779e9667122655a7d2" /><br /><span style="color: #023761; font-weight: bold;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ff55ca5dd8af49a8b6e16db9d0309101" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff55ca5dd8af49a8b6e16db9d0309101}" title="What to pack for skiing"></a></span></p>
<ul>
<li>A selection of 25 green runs and 59 blue runs</li>
<li>Flaine is a slightly smaller resort, but tends to be a little quieter, making learning to use the lifts a more relaxing experience</li>
<li>There are wide and gentle nursery slopes, which are perfect for finding your ski-legs and working up your confidence</li>
<li>If you are a confident beginner, it's worth trying the blue Cristal run - an open and gentle slope that takes you straight back into resort</li>
</ul>
<div class="data-grid" style="text-align: center;"><a style="font-weight: bold;" data-udi="umb://document/5f7cf8fdbd684bd5bba7644eede878ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f7cf8fdbd684bd5bba7644eede878ac}" title="Flaine" class="c-btn">View Flaine</a></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div><em>Some of our resorts do an exclusive ‘</em><strong>Learn to Ski Package</strong><em>’ for Inghams customers.  It’s worth checking during your booking if your resort offers this excellent combined package so you can save some pennies, get high-quality instructors and beat the crowds. </em>
<p> </p>
<h3>Travel with confidence</h3>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<br />
<div> </div>
